<div><head>《新義》</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1474_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1474_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1474_CHANT_001-1a.2">聲音節諧故為之樂，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1474_CHANT_001-1a.3">所以上舞飛雲之鳥，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1474_CHANT_001-1a.4">下躍沈淵之魚。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1474_CHANT_001-1a.5">虞世南《北堂書鈔》卷一百七引劉欽《新義》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1474_CHANT_001-1a.6">夫交接者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1474_CHANT_001-1a.7">人道之本始，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1474_CHANT_001-1a.8">紀綱之大要，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1474_CHANT_001-1a.9">名由之成，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1474_CHANT_001-1a.10">事由之立。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1474_CHANT_001-1a.11">歐陽詢《藝文類聚》卷二十一引劉歆《新義》、《太平御覽》卷四百六引劉欣《新義》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1474_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2a1474_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1474_CHANT_001-2a.2">交之於人也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1474_CHANT_001-2a.3">猶脣齒之相濟。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1474_CHANT_001-2a.4">才非交不用，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1474_CHANT_001-2a.5">名非交不發，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1474_CHANT_001-2a.6">身非交不立。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2a1474_CHANT_001-2a.7">並同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
